# Whitecrest Mushrooms

This API lists all the pickers associated with a site, sends information about hardware status, and shows data about picking, packing, and mushroom growing.

# Group Pickers

## Pickers Collection [/pickers]

A Picker is a single unit consisting of a lift, cart and a packer.

### List all Pickers [GET]

This route displays all Pickers on a site, and includes their name and ID.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "name": "Picker1",
                "id": 1,
            },
            {
                "name": "Picker2",
                "id": 2,
            },
        ]

## Picker [/pickers/{picker_id}]

+ Parameters
    + picker_id (number) - ID of the picker in the form of an integer

### Show a Picker [GET]

This route exposes a single Picker.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "picker_id": 1,

        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /pickers/1

    + Body
        
            {
                "name": "Picker1",
                "level_id": 10,
                
                
            }

