# Group Carts

## Cart [/pickers/{picker_id}/cart]

+ Parameters
    + picker_id (number) - ID of the picker in the form of an integer
    
### Show a cart [GET]

This route exposes a the cart of a single Picker.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "picker_id": "1",
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /pickers/1/cart

    + Body
        
            {
                "id": "1",
                "level": "10",
                
            }
            
